Dear <%= @disburser_request.submitter.full_name  %>,

<%- if @disburser_request.disburser_request_details.any? -%>
  This message is regarding your request for specimens and data from the <%= @disburser_request.repository.name %> repository.
<%- else  -%>
  This message is regarding your request for data from the <%= @disburser_request.repository.name %> repository.
<%- end -%>

If you feel that you have received this message in error, please notify <%= Rails.configuration.custom.app_config['support']['sender_address'] %>.

Your disbursement request submitted on <%= @disburser_request.submitted_at.to_s(:date) %> has been approved.

Please sign in to to view the status of your request as it is processed:

<%= edit_repository_disburser_request_url(@disburser_request.repository, @disburser_request) %>

<%- if @disburser_request.repository.data_coordinators.any? -%>
You may be contacted by the following data coordiantors to facilitate the release of clinical data for your request:
<%- @disburser_request.repository.data_coordinators.each do |data_coordinator| -%>

  <%= data_coordinator.full_name  %>: <%= data_coordinator.email %>
<%- end -%>
<%- end -%>

<%- if @disburser_request.disburser_request_details.any? && @disburser_request.repository.specimen_coordinators.any? -%>
You may be contacted by the following specimen coordinators to facilitate shipping and handling of specimens for your request:
<%- @disburser_request.repository.specimen_coordinators.each do |specimen_coordinator| -%>

  <%=specimen_coordinator.full_name  %>: <%= specimen_coordinator.email %>
<%- end -%>
<%- end -%>

  Thank you for using the <%= @disburser_request.repository.name %> disbursement request system.

We hope that we have met your needs and appreciate any feedback on the process or suggestions for improvement.

You can provide feedback by sending an email to <%= Rails.configuration.custom.app_config['support']['sender_address'] %>.

We look forward to working with you again in the future.

Thank You,

The Disbursement Committee of the <%= @disburser_request.repository.name %> Repository